::Firaxis::
       "NOOOOOOOOOOOO!  METEARA!"  He flies down to her side lifting up her 
head and holding it as she dies.  His eyes flash red as he glares around with 
utter hatred and determination.  "First I will avenge you.  Then they shall 
all leave this world.  This is my solemn promise m'lady."  He gently lays her 
head back on the ground and stands up.  He glances around quickly finally 
spotting the one she had been fighting with unconscious not far away.  He 
walks over to Sanguine's body and stands over her.  He glares at her 
unconscious form.

       "It's too bad I won't get to hear you scream."  He fires a concussion 
missiles directly at her body, the shockwave sending him flying back through 
the air into the trees.  When he recovers he flies into the air above the 
battlefield.  He fires another concussion missile overhead only this time it 
is tinted with bright red to get the attention of those below him.  He raises 
his voice so that it can be heard by all on the battlefield above the weapons 
fire.  "ATTENTION CYBERTRONIANS!  THIS IS YOUR NOTICE!  YOU ARE HEREBY 
EVICTED FROM THIS PLANET!  ANY WHO DO NOT COMPLY WILL BE PROSECUTED TO THE 
FULLEST EXTENT OF MY LAW!  IN THIS CASE THAT IS A DEATH SENTENCE!"

--part1_137.1777549f.2b071530_boundary
